msgctxt "72_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid "A kappa in Kamurocho? I'll drink to that!"
msgstr "¿Un kappa en Kamurocho? ¡Se merece un brindis!"

msgctxt "84_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid "There ain't no such thing as kappas! You were just drunk－\\r\n"
"and still are!"
msgstr "¡Los kappas no existen! Estabas borracho - \\r\n"
"¡y todavía lo estás!"

msgctxt "96_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid "I'm telling you what I saw. It was an alien or something!"
msgstr "Te estoy diciendo que lo vi. ¡Era un extraterrestre o algo así!"

msgctxt "108_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid "There's no such thing as aliens! You're just drunk."
msgstr "¡Los extraterrestres no existen! Solo estás borracho."

msgctxt "120_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid "Well, maybe it was a monster! Ever think of that?\\r\n"
"I mean, shit, you didn't even see it."
msgstr "Bueno, ¡a lo mejor era un monstruo! ¿Nunca lo has pensado?\n"
"Quiero decir, mierda, ni siquiera lo viste."

msgctxt "132_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid "Then what'd it look like, this alien-monster of yours?"
msgstr "Entonces. ¿Cómo dices que se ve este monstruo-alien tuyo?"

msgctxt "144_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid "It was green, and kinda slimy. It lifted the manhole\\r\n"
"cover in Children's Park and glared right at me!"
msgstr "Era verde y algo viscoso. ¡Levantó la tapa de la alcantarilla en el Parque Infantil y me miró fijamente!"

msgctxt "156_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid "That, my friend, was a kappa. You know, those mythical, cucumber-eating critters. Congrats on finding such a fantastic beast."
msgstr "Eso, mi amigo, era un kappa. Ya sabes, esas criaturas míticas que se alimentan de pepinos. Te felicito por haber encontrado una criatura tan fantástica."

msgctxt "168_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid "So, okay, it was a kappa! Doesn't matter what it's called. When I think of that... <Italic>thing</Italic> creeping through the streets, well, it drives a man to drink!"
msgstr "¡Bueno, será un kappa o lo que sea, no importa! Cuando pienso en esa... <Italic>cosa</Italic> paseándose por la calle, bueno, ¡me dan ganas de beber!"

msgctxt "180_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid "I told you, there ain't no such thing as kappas!\\r\n"
"I swear..."
msgstr "¡Ya te dije que los kappas no existen!\\r \n"
"Te lo juro..."

